## Revised Design with Consul Integration

### Migration Framework Integration

We can update the publish function to include migrations as part of the workflow:

```go
func publish(...) {
    return consulClient.RunOnceAction(
        logContext,
        publishSyncKey,
        func() error {
            // Existing code
            published, err := opensearchInternal.PublishIndices(...)
            if err != nil {
                return err
            } else if published {
                // Existing code
                opensearchInternal.PublishTemplatedScripts(...)

                // NEW: Run migrations after successful publish
                err = RunDataMigrations(logContext, noSqlMgmtRepository, consulClient)
                if err != nil {
                    return err
                }
            }
            return nil
        },
        // ...other code remains same
    )
}
